<% if APP_CONFIG["is_sandbox"] %>
Welcome <%= @firstName %>,

Your request for a developer sandbox account has been approved.

Please use the administrative steps below to complete the setup of your development environment.
    1. Open the Provision Landing Zone page from the Admin menu: <%= @portal_link %>
       Select the “Shared Learning Collaborative” Realm.
       Use your email address as your username
    2. Select sample school data to use in your sandbox. Choose between the SLC sample data or supply your own sample Ed-Fi data.
    3. Complete your landing zone setup and upload the corresponding data.
    4. Write your SLC-compatibile applications using the documentation available at <%= @documentation_link %>
    5. Open the Application Registration page, also available from the Admin menu, to register your sandbox applications.

Thank you,
The Shared Learning Collaborative

<% else %>
Welcome <%= @firstName %>,

Your request for an application developer account has been approved.

To get started, register your applications with the Shared Learning Collaborative. You can do this by navigating to Application Registration from the Admin menu at <%= @portal_link %>.

Thank you,

The Shared Learning Collaborative

<% end %>
